{"tid":2044714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"改革警隊淪空談 市長政途堪虞","createTime":"2020-05-31T09:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T09:32:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"83f883a851d2a942540d663f07417dda28f17c66","tid":2044714,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:30:12.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200531/CXCCN3FNKB2A47IQAX7UEV7MRA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200531%2FCXCCN3FNKB2A47IQAX7UEV7MRA%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=4b16f805\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200531%2FCXCCN3FNKB2A47IQAX7UEV7MRA%2F&h=b5ac7762\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200531/CXCCN3FNKB2A47IQAX7UEV7MRA/</a><br />\n<br />\n改革警隊淪空談 市長政途堪虞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FZM7MOM6XC6XOMNKSVHCF6EMFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFZM7MOM6XC6XOMNKSVHCF6EMFM.jpg&h=5af76bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n弗雷<br />\n<br />\n黑人弗洛伊德被白人警員跪頸死亡，令明尼阿波利斯38歲市長弗雷（Jacob Frey）備受關注，他曾任職律師和全職運動員，競選時曾承諾改革警隊，如何處理今次事件將決定其政治前途。<br />\n<br />\n弗雷生於維珍尼亞州，但到明尼阿波利斯跑馬拉松時愛上此地，在2009年於維蘭路華大學畢業後就搬到當地。他任職律師時專門處理民權和就業案件，..........................<br />\n<br />\n明尼蘇達州網頁顯示，2010年至2018年期間，明尼阿波利斯的非裔人口增長36%，即9.5萬人。該市的政治光譜雖偏向自由派，但發生過多宗警員開槍事件，弗雷競選時承諾改革警隊，........................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疫情衝擊 撕裂升級<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：揚言開槍鎮壓 特朗普火上加油<br />\n<br />\n不過有評論認為，隨着明尼阿波利斯爆發騷亂，弗雷的民望已在非白人社群中跌至新低。哈姆萊大學政治科學系教授舒爾茨（David Schultz）指，富裕的白人和大部份為黑人的窮人之間割裂，後者未如前者般能從當地經濟發展中受惠；而面對武肺疫情帶來的經濟衝擊和弗洛伊德之死激發的民怨，能否......................<br />\n<br />\n他日前就成為共和黨籍的總統特朗普的攻擊目標，指他處理騷亂的手法「軟弱」。他同日回應說：「特朗普不明白明尼阿波利斯的力量。我們堅強得很。」<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n美國<br />\n明尼蘇達<br />\n警暴<br />\nJacob Frey"},{"pid":"88665efbacef05fb96140ae1f2b9466293a1fa06","tid":2044714,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/05/30/us/derek-chauvin-george-floyd.html?action=click&amp;module=Spotlight&amp;pgtype=Homepage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2020%2F05%2F30%2Fus%2Fderek-chauvin-george-floyd.html%3Faction%3Dclick%26module%3DSpotlight%26pgtype%3DHomepage&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d4668811\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2020/05/30/us/derek-chauvin-george-floyd.html?action=click&amp;module=Spotlight&amp;pgtype=Homepage</a>"},{"pid":"caf173bb00d8f98709033511e8a596c5e8a7a716","tid":2044714,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T09:32:08.000Z","msg":"民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}